text: Nguyễn Thiện Nhân (born 12 June 1953) is the Secretary of Communist Party of Vietnam in Ho Chi Minh City from 10 May 2017. His previous post was Chairman of the Vietnamese Fatherland Front ==References== Category:Vietnamese communist politicians Category:1953 births Category:People from Ho Chi Minh City
title: Nguyễn Thiện Nhân
